snippet.title: [OpenTaiko new songs showcase] Touhou Arrangements pack showcase
snippet.description:
Include a collaboration with:
Grazepoint: https://grazepoint.bandcamp.com/ https://grazepoint.bandcamp.com/album/touwho https://grazepoint.bandcamp.com/album/touwho-2
TOHO EURO MISSION: https://djtimotei.bandcamp.com/album/toho-euro-mission-02 https://djtimotei.bandcamp.com/album/toho-euro-mission-03

Get OpenTaiko here :
https://github.com/0auBSQ/OpenTaiko

OpenTaiko songs submission form : 
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/17wooH6nc4CExH-yjNiEHIVE62FiP3_nDLLiUM3lDQzM

Twitter: https://twitter.com/OpenTaiko
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/aA8scTvZ6B

Songs showcased on the video:

00:00 - Evil Gala - Moox (Chart by Colin)
https://soundcloud.com/themoox

00:16 - Spread My Wings - DJ Timotei ft. Slothington (Chart by Komi)
 [DJ Timotei (https://www.youtube.com/@DJ_Timotei); Slothington (https://www.youtube.com/@MiAinwav)]

00:31 - レミリア, 私の影 ～ Ｔｈｅ Ｓｃａｒｌｅｔ Ｆｏｇ Ｍａｃｈｉｎｅ Ｉｎｃｉｄｅｎｔ - Jezebel Ciccone (Chart by Komi)
https://darkdandy13.bandcamp.com/

00:46 - Confession - TTL ft. Kanata (Chart by Komi)
 [TTL (https://www.youtube.com/@ttlsound760)]

01:01 - War Zone - WORLDWIDEWOLF feat. Timothy (Chart by Komi)
 [https://takanashikoubou.com/ https://worldwidewolf.bandcamp.com/ https://soundcloud.com/worldwldewolf https://bsky.app/profile/worldwidewolf.bsky.social https://twitter.com/WORLDWlDEWOLF https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWXNd52sTxn9ubwp2ixct6A https://www.youtube.com/@DJ_Timotei https://twitter.com/DJTimotei https://djtimotei.bandcamp.com/] 

01:16 - Journey - DJ Timotei ft. つぅ (Chart by Komi)
 [DJ Timotei (https://www.youtube.com/@DJ_Timotei); つぅ(https://www.youtube.com/@K2ECradle)]

01:31 - Abyss - Taichenko (Chart by Taichenko & Komi)
https://space.bilibili.com/356518101

01:46 - Exterminate - Taichenko (Chart by Taichenko & Komi)
https://space.bilibili.com/356518101

02:01 - Imperfect Cherry Blossom - Whitetail (Chart by Komi)
https://soundcloud.com/whitetail-music https://treepunk.bandcamp.com/ https://www.youtube.com/user/whitetailmusic 

02:16 - Disintegrated Laevatein - Taichenko (Chart by Taichenko & Komi)
https://space.bilibili.com/356518101

02:31 - Cirno in Quarantine - H5 (Chart by bol)
https://linktr.ee/H5Music

02:46 - BLINDED CRITICISM - DeBisco & Zovi (Chart by Komi)
[DeBisco(https://soundcloud.com/debisco https://twitter.com/debiscomusic) Zovi(https://zovi.bandcamp.com/ https://soundcloud.com/zovi https://twitter.com/zovinoise)]
